This src/ directory contains all C++ source code for the pscf++ package.
Each of the subdirectories util/, pscf/, fd1d/, pspc/, and pspg/ contain
source code from a particular C++ namespace or nested namespace. 
Subdirectories util/ and test/ contain the contents of separate github
repositories that are installed as submodules of the pscfpp respository.

Subdirectories:
  util/  general utilities for scientific computation (namespace Util)
  pscf/  shared classes for package pscfp++ (namespace Pscf)
  fd1d/  finite difference one-dimensional SCFT (namespace Pscf::Fd1d)
  pspc/  pseudo-spectral periodic SCFT on a CPU (namespace Pscf::Pspc)
  pspg/  pseudo-spectral periodic SCFT on a GPU (namespace Pscf::Pspc)
  test/  unit testing framework (base classes)
  draft/ unfinished or unused software drafts 

Files (after running the setup script):
  makefile  - main makefile for in-source compilation
  config.mk - main configuration file for in-source compilation
  configure - script for managing optional features
